  "text": "# COMPLAINTS & SUPPORT  \n**Q: What if I'm unhappy with FirstUK Bank?**\nA: We want to fix it. Contact us:\n- **Phone:** 0800-555-2265\n- **Email:** support@firstuk.bank\n- **Branch:** Visit any location  \n**Q: What's the complaint process?**\nA:\n1. Report issue to us (phone/email/branch)\n2. We investigate (typically 8 days)\n3. We respond with decision and next steps\n4. If unresolved, escalate to Financial Ombudsman Service (free)  \n**Q: How long does FirstUK take to respond?**\nA: Within 8 calendar days (or up to 8 weeks if complex).  \n**Q: Can I complain to Financial Ombudsman?**\nA: Yes, if you're unhappy with our response. They're free and independent.\n- **Phone:** 0800 023 4567\n- **Website:** www.financialombudsman.org.uk  \n---",
